node.text: it’s fuckin @canna4climate day bitches!!!! me and my friends got outside and cleaned up a couple areas in Long Beach to celebrate our new stoner holiday. this post is me encouraging you to get out there today if you’re able!!! us stoners get a bad rep (from decades of propaganda lol) BUT we can start changing the stigma by doing our part to help the planet. happy 4/21 y’all ❤️
